WATSON v. WARDEN OF THE MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 48,

September Term, 1961.]

Decided March 27, 1962.

Before Bruñe, C. J., and Henderson, PIorney, Marbury, and Sybert, JJ.

Per Curiam.

Application for leave to appeal from a denial of post conviction relief is denied for the reasons set out in the opinion of the court below.
